00:14:49.795 --> 00:14:56.790 align:middle line:90%


00:14:56.790 --> 00:14:59.760 align:middle line:84%
>> Childbirth in the public
system or in the hospital

00:14:59.760 --> 00:15:01.770 align:middle line:84%
system, it's not
public hospitals--

00:15:01.770 --> 00:15:03.750 align:middle line:90%
