weekly in the last few weeks.

00:16:31.300 --> 00:16:38.970 align:middle line:84%
And I felt so loved and
embraced and empowered by her.

00:16:38.970 --> 00:16:41.140 align:middle line:90%
She filled me with confidence.

00:16:41.140 --> 00:16:43.950 align:middle line:90%
She was absolutely a realist.

00:16:43.950 --> 00:16:49.867 align:middle line:84%
But she just made me
feel completely capable.

00:16:49.867 --> 00:16:52.200 align:middle line:84%
>> The midwifery care that I
received and that I've been

00:16:52.200 --> 00:16:56.520 align:middle line:84%
a passionate advocate for is
about empowering that woman,

00:16:56.520 --> 00:17:01.260 align:middle line:84%
educating and supporting that
woman for that transformative

00:17:01.260 --> 00:17:05.490 align:middle line:84%
event, to actually enter
motherhood as a strong,

00:17:05.490 --> 00:17:11.339 align:middle line:84%
confident, supported woman, and
then to create that new family.

00:17:11.339 --> 00:17:16.619 align:middle line:84%
>> It's fantastic to support
her and watch how that supports

00:17:16.619 --> 00:17:20.970 align:middle line:84%
empowers her to do what is
probably the most fantastic

00:17:20.970 --> 00:17:22.890 align:middle line:84%
thing she'll ever do,
to birth her baby.

00:17:22.890 --> 00:17:24.818 align:middle line:90%
