00:17:24.818 --> 00:17:27.073 align:middle line:90%


00:17:27.073 --> 00:17:28.740 align:middle line:84%
>> I remember Maggie
the midwife saying,

00:17:28.740 --> 00:17:31.237 align:middle line:84%
when the baby comes out,
nobody tell her what it is.

00:17:31.237 --> 00:17:32.445 align:middle line:90%
Let her find out for herself.

00:17:32.445 --> 00:17:36.100 align:middle line:90%


00:17:36.100 --> 00:17:38.240 align:middle line:84%
I just remember this
extraordinary feeling

00:17:38.240 --> 00:17:41.720 align:middle line:90%
of my pelvis opening.

00:17:41.720 --> 00:17:44.088 align:middle line:84%
It was the most amazing
thing I've ever experienced.

00:17:44.088 --> 00:17:46.130 align:middle line:84%
And I was sorry it didn't
happen the second time.

00:17:46.130 --> 00:17:48.380 align:middle line:84%
It just kind of popped
out the second time.

00:17:48.380 --> 00:17:51.380 align:middle line:84%
But this feeling
of your whole self

00:17:51.380 --> 00:17:53.930 align:middle line:84%
just expanding and
expanding and expanding

00:17:53.930 --> 00:17:56.810 align:middle line:90%
to let this person out.

00:17:56.810 --> 00:18:01.170 align:middle line:84%
And then the minute
his head was out,

00:18:01.170 --> 00:18:03.600 align:middle line:84%
