And there was an
almighty clap of thunder.

00:18:14.740 --> 00:18:16.740 align:middle line:90%
And there were eight witnesses.

00:18:16.740 --> 00:18:18.820 align:middle line:90%
It wasn't just me going nuts.

00:18:18.820 --> 00:18:21.050 align:middle line:84%
So loud that she was saying,
