going to pick him up?

00:18:33.560 --> 00:18:35.610 align:middle line:90%
Oh, and I said, is it a boy?

00:18:35.610 --> 00:18:38.750 align:middle line:84%
And she said, yes,
it's a boy, damn it.

00:18:38.750 --> 00:18:39.710 align:middle line:90%
Sorry I told you.

00:18:39.710 --> 00:18:43.170 align:middle line:84%
Anyway, I picked him up, put
him straight on the breast.

00:18:43.170 --> 00:18:48.440 align:middle line:84%
I was desperate for a
coffee for some reason.

00:18:48.440 --> 00:18:52.370 align:middle line:84%
And the house, for three
days with both births,

00:18:52.370 --> 00:18:55.100 align:middle line:84%
the house felt like there
were angels around it.

00:18:55.100 --> 00:18:58.530 align:middle line:84%
The atmosphere in the
