hospital and have a Cesarean.

01:09:00.920 --> 01:09:02.439 align:middle line:90%
I think it's just as important.

01:09:02.439 --> 01:09:04.010 align:middle line:90%
It's just as valid.

01:09:04.010 --> 01:09:05.960 align:middle line:84%
And wouldn't it be
radical if the government

01:09:05.960 --> 01:09:09.840 align:middle line:84%
supported all women to have
the births that they choose?

01:09:09.840 --> 01:09:11.840 align:middle line:84%
And why aren't we
lobbying for that?

